{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_24015.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story06","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":3.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20073.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"...A red moon...@Is this someone's mind?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"It seems so."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Torte, you said that@the moon was red in your era."},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Is it always like this in the 15th century?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Yeah... Though it seems it didn't used to be like this."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"It's dark... It's a little scary."},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"It's nighttime, [chara:831303:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:831303:cheek_0][chara:831303:face_mtn_ex_010.exp3.json][chara:831303:lipSynch_1]but it should be dawn soon."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"...Is that so? You've got a good understanding."},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Until dawn, should we rest for a bit?@It's safe inside the magic circle."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"M-magic circle? Can you create one?!"},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Yeah!"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"I have tools I took from my parents' workshop!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_20071.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime02","chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"It's dawn...!","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Alright, let's head towards the populated area!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"...Hey, Torte, is there a reason","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"why you're investigating Jeanne?"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"...Yeah."},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Everyone usually calls me Torte,"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"but my real name is Jeanne."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":831303,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"My mother said my name came from La Pucelle."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"I see... That would make you curious,@wouldn't it?"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"When you hear that someone else@was the basis for your name..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Right? Additionally, it seems my face@resembles La Pucelle a lot!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Is that so...?"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Yeah! That's why, before becoming a Magical Girl,"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"I want to learn various things about my respected@senior."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"...You want to become...a Magical Girl...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"I have the potential for it."},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Qube has been following me all along."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"But my mother said"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"that I can only wish for a miracle once, so I@must think carefully and make my decision."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Qube..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"You are talking about Kyubey, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Ah, wait, can you also see Kyubey?"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Ah... Yeah..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Wow, we're the same! Best regards!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"I see, it's Kyubey... The name differs depending@on the language."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Probably... That's what I think...@[chara:102001:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:102001:cheek_0][chara:102001:face_mtn_ex_050.exp3.json][chara:102001:lipSynch_1]Oh, wait!"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Speaking of language...@How come we can understand each other?!"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":831303,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"That's thanks to the magic stones I have!"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Magic stones...?"},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"That's right!"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Here, I'll give you one too, Kagome."},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"With this, you should be able to interview anyone@you meet!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Oh... Thank you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"...In the end, whose mind is this place?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Who knows?"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Someone who knows Jeanne d'Arc..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"...@..."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51158_tower_tart2/memoria_1733.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"surround":"7023_camera"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_20071.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime16","chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Huh...?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"pos":2}],"na